Yes — your tests are failing because `moveIfExists(...)` no longer calls `doesObjectExist(...)` with:

```java
"failed/file.zip.pgp"
```

It now calls it with:

```java
"test-bucket/failed/file.zip.pgp"
```

And it also delegates to `moveFile(...)` instead of directly calling `copyObject(...)` and `deleteObject(...)`.

So the tests need to change to match that.

