## Why this fixes the failure

Your failing stub was:

```java
when(s3Client.doesObjectExist("test-bucket", "failed/file.zip.pgp"))
```

But the code now calls:

```java
s3Client.doesObjectExist("test-bucket", "test-bucket/failed/file.zip.pgp")
```

So Mockito reported a strict stubbing mismatch.

